<br>
The best tank should be the person that's hardest to get aggro.  Like others have said, taunt works fine in PoP.  It's not like having AE Taunt refresh every 5 seconds but it works enough that you can rely on it.  Yes it's not always going to work but it's up to the rest of the people to manage their aggro as well.  Warriors should not be able to get aggro at will (except AE taunt) by the virtue of we still being the best tanks.  If the best tank can get aggro at will, then aggro management aspect of the game is trivial, and this is a pretty big aspect of the game. <p><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=90049">Phantron</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top">  Page <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthearena.showMessageRange?topicID=2568.topic&start=1&stop=20>1</a><a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthearena.showMessageRange?topicID=2568.topic&start=21&stop=40>2</a><a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthearena.showMessageRange?topicID=2568.topic&start=41&stop=60>3</a> <b>4</b>  </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthearena.showPrevMessage?topicID=2568.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthearena.showNextMessage?topicID=2568.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthearena.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=2568.topic&index=74><img src=http://www.steelwarrior.org/forum/swaddreply.GIF border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthearena.emailToFriend?topicID=2568.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fth